      <title>澳大利亚总理称X反对拆除教堂刺杀柱的斗争“非同寻常”</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-pm-calls-xs-fight-against-removal-church-stabbing-posts-extraordinary-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，社交媒体平台 X 在法庭上对网络监管机构删除一些有关悉尼主教被刺伤的帖子的命令提出质疑，澳大利亚总理安东尼·阿尔巴内塞 (Anthony Albanese) 称这一决定“非同寻常”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australian-pm-calls-xs-fight-against-removal-church-stabbing-posts-extraordinary-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 04:04:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着国内规则收紧，中国量化基金向海外扩张</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-quant-funds-expand-abroad-rules-tighten-home-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着国内竞争加剧以及监管机构加强对这个 2600 亿美元行业的审查，中国数据驱动的量化交易基金正在海外迅速扩张。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/chinese-quant-funds-expand-abroad-rules-tighten-home-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 03:57:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>官员表示，中国致力于通过对话解决海上争端</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-is-committed-resolving-maritime-disputes-through-talks-official-says-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，一名高级军事官员在港口城市青岛举行的外国海军高级官员会议上表示，中国仍然致力于通过对话解决与其他国家的海上争端，但不会允许自己被“滥用”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/china-is-committed-resolving-maritime-disputes-through-talks-official-says-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 03:19:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马来西亚规划东南亚最大集成电路设计园</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/malaysia-offer-incentives-attract-global-tech-companies-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[马来西亚政府周一表示，计划建设东南亚最大的集成电路设计园区，并将提供税收减免、补贴和免签证费等激励措施，以吸引全球科技公司和投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/malaysia-offer-incentives-attract-global-tech-companies-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:55:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>救援人员争先恐后地救助中国广东省洪水被困的人们</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rescuers-race-reach-those-trapped-by-floods-chinas-guangdong-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在中国遭受洪水蹂躏的广东省，救援人员迅速撤离被困居民，将一些老人从家中背出来，并出动直升机救援陷入农村山体滑坡的村民。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/rescuers-race-reach-those-trapped-by-floods-chinas-guangdong-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:49:41 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>亚洲股市小幅上涨，石油和黄金因中东担忧情绪缓和而回落</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[亚洲股市周一收复部分失地，债券收益率上涨，因对更广泛的中东冲突的担忧消退，投资者重新转向风险较高的资产。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:42:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>腾讯将于5月推出《地下城与勇士》手游</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencent-release-dungeon-fighter-mobile-game-may-after-seven-years-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国科技巨头腾讯控股周一表示，经过七年的开发，备受期待的《地下城与勇士》手游将于5月21日发布。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/tencent-release-dungeon-fighter-mobile-game-may-after-seven-years-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:35:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>麦格理银行部门将停止新车贷款，专注于抵押贷款增长</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/macquaries-banking-unit-stop-new-car-loans-focus-mortgage-growth-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚金融集团麦格理集团周一表示，其银行和金融服务部门将停止通过直接、经纪人和创新租赁渠道发放新车贷款，以优先考虑住房贷款和存款业务的增长。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/finance/macquaries-banking-unit-stop-new-car-loans-focus-mortgage-growth-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 02:29:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>激烈竞争导致盈利前景下调，新西兰航空股价下跌</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-new-zealand-falls-after-earnings-outlook-cut-stiff-competition-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新西兰航空周一下调了年度盈利预期，理由是经济逆风和生活成本危机导致国内和北美市场收入疲软，导致该公司股价跌至近两年低点。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/aerospace-defense/air-new-zealand-falls-after-earnings-outlook-cut-stiff-competition-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 01:40:56 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾和美军开始年度作战演习</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-troops-begin-annual-combat-drills-2024-04-22/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[近 17,000 名菲律宾和美国军队将于周一在菲律宾开始为期三周的联合作战训练演习，其中包括在南中国海进行海上演习，马尼拉和北京在南海海域边界问题上发生了争执。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/philippines-us-troops-begin-annual-combat-drills-2024-04-22/</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 00:51:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
